_______________________________________________________________________________
"Imprint"         
        This imprints an object with the psionicist's "psychic
        signature".  If cast in most places on the mud it will last a
        temporary amount of time dependent on guild level. If cast in
        the storage  room of the Psionicist Guild it has a permanent
        duration (until the item is next picked up).  It will not
        allow anybody but the psionicist to pick up the item.
 
SP Cost:  3		Guild Level:  2		Potential Points:  1
 
Command:  imprint <object>
